<span class="index">4.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_4_151075" id="refIndex_4_151075" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[4]_151075">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/2727976/9a997UPcVaS4YL2UcLabw8MwHL_OepgurbtqQS_PtxQzHiae232NfmT0JG-UvYsPJlNN5VuKPUGr1tRF5mYGMMx57Ta0UibGfDAMGauQPwfpmX2GwQ" target="_blank" class="text">中国经济网<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type1 " id="reference-[5]-151075-wrap">
<span class="index">5.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_5_151075" id="refIndex_5_151075" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[5]_151075">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/2727976/9c61SLTxAHFhwnCKA-D94xSF91ZncnozGg10NQomdZ4b_bel4J77uay9YP5kK18VCxv-gNvAVY5sbfulKYGIaNFsg6MphbaTpLtlBBOSui92qg" target="_blank" class="text">血燕亚硝酸盐严重超标<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type2 " id="reference-[6]-151075-wrap">
<span class="index">6.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_6_151075" id="refIndex_6_151075" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[6]_151075">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<span>史贤明</span><span class="text">．食品安全与卫生学</span><span>．北京</span><span>：中国农业出版社</span><span>，2002</span></li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type1 " id="reference-[7]-151075-wrap">
<span class="index">7.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_7_151075" id="refIndex_7_151075" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[7]_151075">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/2727976/4908tzIds0z_YDg9fmU2oA2VC_xO7kTKtQSPdbygP0NmvOWsw0bo9zLtVZl7pP9GgBUitJU6XtAfBga8TvvjZVFhXXr8_joBPt1V9eCv_um02DMgubb76kYHD-YJpk8y-g" target="_blank" class="text">专家解析亚硝酸盐的“善与恶”<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
</li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type1 " id="reference-[8]-151075-wrap">
<span class="index">8.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_8_151075" id="refIndex_8_151075" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[8]_151075">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/2727976/6701gUun7emEhRT_RPRAG-TxkXdv44EdxsdJQJNKkRUx_UsBLLT-9WLAqj1PxylWx-SoZL7C7PLlXmJO0VwNqse_NnENGHS3" target="_blank" class="text">香港市售燕窝全部含亚硝酸盐 最严重超标31倍，2011年09月23日<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
</li></ul>
</dd>
</dl>
